        <ul>
          <li>All documents from employment visa category</li>
          <li><a href="/personal/immigration/bank/">Bank statements</a> (6 months, showing qualifying deposits)</li>
          <li>Property ownership documents (if applicable)</li>
          <li>Business license and trade documents (if entrepreneur category)</li>
          <li>See our complete <a href="/services/golden-visa-translation/">Golden Visa translation package</a></li>
